Floorp is available in `nixpkgs` primarily as a binary package (`floorp-bin`)[3][4]. While there is a `programs.floorp` module in Home Manager (which mirrors the structure of the Firefox module), it is less commonly used than the standard `programs.firefox` module and may have limitations depending on your version[5][6][7].

